name: Website Exclusive: 14K Gold Filled Swarovski Crystal Wire Wrapped Earring (Tanzanite Purple)
description:
Simple:: Pretty:: Everyday Jewellery

14K Gold Fill and Swarovski Crystal beads are free style wire wrapped creating the perfect pair of  earrings that are perfect for everyday wear, summer wedding jewelry, Beach wedding jewellery, Bridesmaid gift, vacation jewelry or as a gift for a special lady in your life.

*Measurements: 
* Approx. 6mm wide x 26mm long from top of the to the bottom of the earrings 

What is 14K Gold Filled? 
Pure gold is 24K and is so soft that is it impossible to utilize it in wire wrap jewellery.
Gold Filled / Rolled gold is created by taking a sheet of 14K Gold and bonding it through extreme heat and pressure to a core of semi-precious metal (brass). This is a very sophisticated process and only a few mills in the world do it. Gold-filled products are resistant to tarnishing because the outside layer is actually gold and is thick enough to prevent oxidation of the inner material. It is not a yellowy color, rather it is a beautiful mild gold color ~ a very beautiful, versatile and affordable alternative to solid gold.

*All Components are 14K Gold Filled

*Due to the handmade nature of each piece I design, there may be slight variations in size from piece to piece.

*Colors may vary due to individual monitor settings
